# ============================================================
# TIMELINE DETAIL POLICY
# ============================================================

status: canonical
layer: policy
domain: detail
subdomain: timeline-detail
system: civilization-os
owner: Boss
prepared_by: Zero

purpose:
Defines policy rules for timeline detail.

policy_focus:
- current versus historical mode separation
- cancellation-state labeling
- replay-safe retention policy
- milestone disclosure boundaries

disclosure_matrix:
- current_progression: current-mode only
- historical_replay: history mode only
- cancelled_stage_history: history/audit mode only
- sealed_timeline_trace: explicit authority required

validation_rules:
- cancelled or historical stages must not appear as current progression.
- replay output must remain explicitly labeled.
